               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir "The Five Pillars of Mystery" (fols. 5r-34r) &#xD;
I-1) Introduction (fols. 3r-16v) &#xD;
I-2) Mǝśṭira Śǝllāse “Mystery of the Trinity” (fols. 16v-38r) &#xD;
I-3) Mǝśṭira śǝggāwe “Mystery of the Incarnation” (fols. 38r-63r) &#xD;
I-4) Mǝśṭira ṭǝmqat “Mystery of Baptism” (fols. 63r-79r) &#xD;
I-5) Mǝśṭira qʷǝrbān “Mystery of the Eucharist” (fols. 79r-93r &#xD;
I-6) Mǝśṭira tǝnśāʾe mutān “Mystery of the Resurrection of the Dead” (fols. 93r-109r)</summary>
